  "notes": [
    "deck_geojson 仍然是 legacy 图，metadata 明确声明 `useLegacyApi=true`，真实请求路径是 `/superset/explore_json/`。",
    "`/superset/explore_json/` 路径会读取原始 `form_data`，补 `datasource`，然后执行 `convert_legacy_filters_into_adhoc(form_data)` 与 `merge_extra_filters(form_data)`。",
    "当前源码里 `Guest user cannot modify chart payload` 只在 `security/manager.py::raise_for_access(query_context=...)` 分支触发，核心比较器是 `query_context_modified()`；legacy `/superset/explore_json/` 则会走 `views/utils.py::check_datasource_perms()` -> `get_viz()` -> `viz.raise_for_access()` -> `security/manager.py::raise_for_access(viz=self)`。当前 `viz` 分支会校验 `dashboardId` / `slice_id` / datasource 绑定，但没有等价的 columns / metrics / orderby 子集比较器。",
    "即便如此，deck_geojson 的查询列、颜色覆盖、GeoJsonLayer 视觉参数、地图样式、viewport 和自定义 JS 都直接来自 root form_data。最稳妥的 embedding 策略仍然是根层复制保存态图表，只把动态筛选放进 `extra_form_data`。",
    "`crossFiltersDataMask.ts` 对 `formData.geojson` 的分支不会产生普通列过滤，而是构造一个 SQL 表达式列 `REPLACE(<geojson列>, ' ', '')`，再用 `LIKE '%<geometry coordinates json>%` 的方式放进 `extraFormData.filters`。",
    "`Geojson.tsx` 会直接读取 `fill_color_picker` / `stroke_color_picker`。所以 embedding 场景下也不能只复制查询字段；整套保存态视觉字段都应该保留。"
  ],
  "security_enforcement": {
    "frontend_request_mode": "legacy explore_json",
    "frontend_request_endpoint": "/superset/explore_json/",
    "frontend_request_payload": {
      "form_data": "<raw form_data>"
    },
    "backend_normalization_steps": [
      "convert_legacy_filters_into_adhoc(form_data)",
      "merge_extra_filters(form_data)"
    ],
    "verified_guest_payload_guard": {
      "chart_data_api": "security/manager.py::query_context_modified",
      "chart_data_api_error": "Guest user cannot modify chart payload",
      "legacy_explore_json_api": "`check_datasource_perms()` 会构造 viz 并调用 `raise_for_access(viz=self)`；该分支校验 datasource / dashboard / slice 绑定，但没有 `query_context_modified()` 那种 query subset guard",
      "confidence": "high"
    },
    "guest_access_binding_fields": [
      "dashboardId",
      "slice_id"
    ],
    "query_critical_root_fields": [
      "slice_id",
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "geojson",
      "row_limit",
      "filter_nulls",
      "adhoc_filters",
      "mapbox_style",
      "viewport",
      "autozoom",
      "fill_color_picker",
      "stroke_color_picker",
      "filled",
      "stroked",
      "extruded",
      "line_width",
      "line_width_unit",
      "point_radius_scale",
      "js_columns",
      "js_data_mutator",
      "js_tooltip",
      "js_onclick_href"
    ],
    "recommended_strategy": "复制保存态 chart form_data 作为 base，仅通过 extra_form_data 追加动态过滤条件；不要在 embedding 请求里重构 deck_geojson 的 root 查询字段和图表定义字段。"
  },
  "safe_base_rule": {
    "description": "第三方 embedding 请求中的根层 form_data，应当从已保存的 deck_geojson 图表直接复制，不要自行重构。",
    "must_be_copied_from_saved_chart": [
      "slice_id",
      "dashboardId",
      "datasource",
      "viz_type",
      "geojson",
      "row_limit",
      "filter_nulls",
      "adhoc_filters",
      "mapbox_style",
      "viewport",
      "autozoom",
      "fill_color_picker",
      "stroke_color_picker",
      "filled",
      "stroked",
      "extruded",
      "line_width",
      "line_width_unit",
      "point_radius_scale",
      "js_columns",
      "js_data_mutator",
      "js_tooltip",
      "js_onclick_href",
      "all other saved chart-definition fields"
    ],
    "why": [
      "deck_geojson 没有专属前端 buildQuery，前端会把 root form_data 直接发给 `/superset/explore_json/`。",
      "`DeckGeoJson.query_obj()` / `DeckGeoJson.get_properties()` 会直接消费 root `geojson`。",
      "`Geojson.tsx` 会直接消费 root `fill_color_picker`、`stroke_color_picker`、`filled`、`stroked`、`extruded`、`line_width`、`line_width_unit`、`point_radius_scale`、`mapbox_style` 和 `viewport`。",
      "`merge_extra_filters()` 会在后端把 `extra_form_data` 并入 legacy 请求，因此动态筛选不需要通过覆盖根层保存态字段来实现。",
      "虽然当前没有在 legacy 路径定位到 `query_context_modified()` 等价校验，但复制保存态仍然是最稳妥、最接近官方前端行为的策略。"
    ]
  },
